name: Serie Tribute: 12 - Mister Negative
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

First appearance: Free Comic Book Day: The Amazing Spider-Man #1 (May 2007)
Mister Negative came into conflict with Spider-Man when he made a power play to take control of New York's criminal underworld, attempting to wipe out all existing members of the Karnelli and Maggia crime families using a specific DNA bio-weapon called the "Devil's Breath."
As a result of his exposure to the D-Lite drug, Mister Negative can generate and control Darkforce and Lightforce, manifesting it as the photographic negative of black or white electrical energy. He uses this unique form of Darkforce for a variety of purposes.
